SIMPLE: monomania
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Monomania
<hw>Mon`o*ma"ni*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Mono-</ets> + <ets>mania</ets>.]</ety> <def>Derangement of
the mind in regard of a single subject only; also, such a concentration
of interest upon one particular subject or train of ideas to show mental
derangement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Insanity; madness; alienation; aberration;
derangement; mania. See <er>Insanity</er>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monomaniac</ent>⟦br⟧
